(34, 1, 6, 'Биопурит (BioPurit)', 'Биопурит', 'biopurit_flotenk', 'uploads/images/cat-34-4.jpg', NULL, '<h2>The CFPB strives to better serve consumers by using plain language; relying on simple, user-friendly design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The CFPB strives to better serve consumers by using plain language; relying on simple, user-friendly design; and providing easy access to information that can help consumers <a href=\"http://kolos-spb.ru/articles/septik_pod_kluch.html#content\">make informed decisions</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n<figure class=\"image\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"33\" height=\"333\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539860033517-9dcef150c133?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&amp;ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&amp;s=ec5ac6ffaf5ab9d7513fe8f4bc64ad49&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;q=60\" width=\"500\" />\r\n<figcaption>This Design Manual is an open-source resource for CFPB</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>This Design Manual is an open-source resource for CFPB staff to produce effective and visually-consistent products that are easy for consumers to access, use, and understand. The Manual includes our design principles, guidelines for user experience, visual identity standards, and code snippets for common user interface elements. The Manual will continue to evolve as we learn what works best for the CFPB and the people we serve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5NV6Rdv1a3I\" width=\"640\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Minicon homepage image</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Help us make improvements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"93\" src=\"/uploads/saulo-mohana-78181-unsplash.jpg\" style=\"float:left\" width=\"140\" />We have designed the Manual to be open for the public, which allows you to help us make improvements by filing an issue or submitting a pull request on GitHub. Not on GitHub? Email us your suggestions at tech@consumerfinance.gov .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All content has been released as open source under the CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication, and we&rsquo;d love for other agencies, developers, or groups to adapt it for their own use.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Other Resources</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We are proud to join the community of organizations that have made their design standards public</li>\r\n	<li>such as Mozilla</li>\r\n	<li>the BBC and the UK&#39;s Government Digital Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>We hope our design manual can serve as a foundation for discussing and practicing user-centered design in government.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<h3>Other Resources</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>We are proud to join the community of organizations that have made their design standards public</li>\r\n	<li>such as Mozilla</li>\r\n	<li>the BBC and the UK&#39;s Government Digital Service</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We hope our design manual can serve as a foundation for discussing and practicing user-centered design in government.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Landing page types provide an overview of a main navigation section and helps users situate themselves within the site and the</p>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"image\" style=\"float:right\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"99\" src=\"/uploads/vrezka-trubi-mini.JPG\" width=\"132\" />\r\n<figcaption>Front-End Style Guide</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>subject matter. Their main function is to preview the different sub-pages within that section and help users quickly skim section topics and select the category that interests them.&nbsp;Landing page types provide an overview of a main navigation section and helps users situate themselves within the site and the subject matter. Their main function is to preview the different sub-pages within that section and help users quickly skim section topics and select the category that interests them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hedwig is Posten and Brings Front-End Style Guide.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Posten and Bring must</